      "raw_text": "The mill and lumber workers con-\nSention at Occur dAlene City ad-\njourned yesterday. 1t was deemed\nadvisable to take no action for the\npresent in the matter of fixing a uni\nform wage scale.\n\n\nThe object of the convention was\nto discuss the question of wages and\nbeyond that no other subject was\nconsidered. The delegates reported\nthat the logging camps in the vicinity\nof Occur dAlene are we'll organized."
